Text.string: Hey, you. Come here.
Payback's all I got.
What are you talkin' about? That was Drunk Darryl, and he did it on a dare! You can't be takin' credit for that!
Nah, man! Drunk Darryl was this guy who blew himself up siphoning methanol from a Pyrotech's flamethrower.
Oh, you know what? You're right. I was gettin' those mixed up. You did make that guy melt. Mad props.
Damn right!
I fragged all those dumb supplies! Ha-ha! I'm a menace to society! Vault Hunter, you gonna come kill me or what?!
No way! I destroyed those supplies! I'm history's greatest monster! If anyone deserves a Vault Hunter coming after them, it's me!
I... honestly don't know which one is horrible enough to have murdered my family. Uh, just pick one to kill, I guess. I'll consider that my payback. I trust your judgment.
Just killin' some time, killin' some dudes!
Walk the plank, idiot!
Gahghhghh!

Right, so... as you can see, life sucks right now. There's these two Maliwan guys, Rax and Max, who are crapping it up in particular. It's like they're trying to out-war-crime each other. One of them murdered my family—I don't know who. Find out who did it and kill 'em.
Ahahaha! Splat!
Ah, that never gets old.
It's the Vault Hunter! Kill me! I'm the worst!
No, kill me, Vault Hunter! I'M the worst!
Aw, man. I thought I was the worst.
Come ON! I was WAY worse!
Yeah, yeah! It WAS that guy! Screw him! Thanks, Vault Hunter. I can finally rest knowing my family has been avenged. Probably. Come back and get your reward.
Ughhh. Now I'm second guessing myself. That other guy seemed pretty family-murdery too. There's still a chance it was him. Maybe you could go kill him, just in case?
No? Okay. I guess I'll spend the rest of my life knowing there's a fifty-fifty chance my family's killer is still out there. But yeah, sure. You did great, Vault Hunter. Probably.
Changed your mind, huh? I knew it! I'm the worst after all!
Hey! Did that stupid civ tell you I killed their family? Well... I totally did! I'm the worst there's ever been! Guess you gotta kill ME! Hey, Max! Look who's got a Vault Hunter after 'em!
So you figured out I'm the worst after all! Yeah! Let's do this!
Okay! All bases covered! You definitely avenged my family somewhere in all that. Come back and get your reward, Vault Hunter.
Payback! You're a killin' machine, Vault Hunter. Thanks for taking the endless cycle of bloodshed onto your shoulders. Now I'm out of it! Here, this should help make up for your bloody shoulders.

What?! No way! I killed that family. Vault Hunter, come after me, not Rax! That idiot couldn't kill a litter of bunnies if he had a custom belt-fed bunny-mulcher! Which he doesn't! Because I have that!
Ugh! These guys BOTH suck ass, which means we can't trust either of 'em. You gotta figure out who killed who if I'm gonna get my revenge.
Yep, that right there is where I did all those family-murders. Just chopped 'em up, and threw them indiscriminately into those body bags like a gunky trail mix.
That was so awesome... when I did it! It was me, Vault Hunter! I did those murders and they were all super horrible! I should be the target!
This only proves Maliwan killed my family, not that Rax or Max did it. My family was stashing supplies in a vehicle nearby—see if there's any clues there.
Vault Hunter. Seriously, I'm the worst! One time I made a guy drink that green goo inside a corrosive barrel! Dude MELTED! Saw his SKULL and stuff!
